  description="AI has collapsed the time cost of CRO analysis. What used to require a team of five now takes one specialist with the right setup. Here's what that means for how serious brands should hire."
  canonicalUrl="https://hichembennaceur.com/blog/cro-in-the-ai-era-2026"
